content.rendered:
The young woman, Naru, was raised among the greatest hunters to ever roam the Great Plains. Knowing that he is as talented as the other young hunters, he sets out to protect his people from the threat to the Comanche camp. Armed with primitive tools, Naru follows him and then engages with his prey, which turns out to be a highly developed extraterrestrial predator with modern weapons, and their encounter ends in a fierce and merciless showdown between the two enemies.

Directed By Dan Trachtenberg

Written By Patrick Aison. Dan Trachtenberg. Jim Thomas

Stars: Amber Midthunder. Dakota Beavers. Dane DiLiegro
